  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 4th tier, you adopt a particular style of design for your ship.</p><h3>Probe</h3><p><span style=\"font-family:'Open Sans', sans-serif\">Your ship gains the Stealth Device modification at no cost.</span></p><p>Additionally, when your ship attempts to conceal on its turn, it can opt to not move on that turn causing creatures that attempt to detect your ship to take a -10 penalty to their Wisdom (Scan) checks until the start of your ship's next turn. Your ship loses this benefit if it moves, either voluntarily or because of some external effect.</p>",
